Much of the business world operates on PDFs. Even when there are APIs and web tools, PDFs invariably find their way into any process where humans are involved. Build a simple website where I can upload a PDF and it shows me the extracted text from the PDF. 

Tech Stack:
-HTML
-TailwindCSS
-Python(flask)

Rules:
-The website should be appealing and functional.
- Make sure to add error handling.
- Organize python files in a folder called "Libraries" except app.py
- organize all files to industry standards